Wasu 'yan majalisa sun yi mamakin shawarar da aka yi musu na canja sunan ofishinsu zuwa MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament).
Wannan batun ya samo asali ne daga wani shiri na sauya sunan majalisar dokokin kasar zuwa majalisar dokokin Wales.
'Yan majalisa daga bangarorin siyasa daban-daban na Majalisar Dokoki ta Kasa sun nuna damuwa kan yadda za a yi ba'a a majalisa.
Wani dan majalisa a jam'iyyar Labour ya ce 'yan takararsa sun damu saboda kalmar da ta yi karin magana a kai ta ce 'Twp' da 'Pwp'.
Ga masu karatu a waje da Wales, kalmar yaren Welsh daft tana nufin 'mai tsananin kai' kuma pwp tana nufin 'sharar gida'.
Wani da ke cikin rukunin ya ce, "Ba mu yi farin ciki ba" kuma ya ce za a ba da wasu sunaye.
Wani dan jam'iyyar Conservative Party of Wales ya ce kungiyarsa tana "karbar" da sunan, amma ya yi nuni da cewa "MWP" yana da kama da "Muppet".
Alal misali, yadda ake furta w a yaren Hausa ya yi kama da yadda ake furta u a yaren Yorkshire.
Kwamitin Majalisar Dokoki ta Kasa, wanda a yanzu yake tsara dokar da ta shafi sauya sunan, ya ce: Tabbas, yan majalisa ne za su yanke hukunci na karshe kan duk sunayen da za a kira 'yan majalisar.
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017 ta ba Majalisar Dokokin Wales damar canza sunan ta.
A watan Yuni, hukumar ta wallafa sakamakon binciken da aka gudanar na jama'a kan sunan da aka gabatar, wanda ya nuna cewa akwai goyon baya ga sauya sunan majalisar zuwa majalisar dokokin Wales.
A kan batun nadin mambobin majalisar, kwamitin ya fi son sunan 'Members of the Welsh Parliament' watau WMPs, amma masu amsa a cikin wani zaɓe na jama'a sun fi son 'MWPs'.
'Yan majalisa za su iya gabatar da wasu sunaye, amma cimma yarjejeniya zai iya zama kalubale ga shugaban kasa Elin Jones, wanda zai gabatar da kudurin da ya shafi canje-canje a cikin makonni masu zuwa.
A cikin wannan tsari, an yi la'akari da cewa an yi wa 'yan majalisu yankan zumunci a cikin majalisa, wanda ya ƙunshi 'yan majalisa da ke da' yanci a cikin majalisa.
A yayin da ake tattauna dokar, 'yan majalisa ne suke da damar yin zaɓe a kan waɗanda za su zama 'yan majalisa.
