Trump ya ce Kavanaugh "ya yi wa'azi ga jam'iyyar Democrat" "a cikin fushi da fushi".
"Tallafawa Alkalin Kavanaugh wata murya ce da za a yi wa 'yan jam'iyyar Democrat, da ke da karfin hali da kuma takunkumi, " in ji Trump a jawabinsa na jin dadi a Wheeling, West Virginia.
