Kanye West: Mai rairayi ya yi amfani da sabon sunansa na "Ye"
Rapper Kanye West ya canza sunansa zuwa "Ye".
A ranar Asabar, wani mutum ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter, sanarwar sauya sheka, ya ce: Kanye West na baya.
An yi wa West mai shekara 41 lakabi da Ye na wani lokaci, kuma ya yi amfani da sunan a matsayin taken kundin wakarsa na takwas da ya fitar a watan Yuni.
Canjin ya faru ne kafin ya bayyana a shirinsa na Saturday Night Live, inda aka sa ran zai gabatar da sabon kundin wakarsa mai suna Yandhi.
Ta maye gurbin Ariana Grant, wadda ta soke waƙar a lokacin da take cikin damuwa, in ji mai shirya shirin.
Ban da cewa gajarta ne na sunan da ake amfani da shi a halin yanzu, West ya ce a baya ya ce kalmar tana da muhimmanci a gare shi a bangaren addini.
"Ina ganin cewa" "ye" tana daya daga cikin kalmomin da aka fi amfani da su a cikin Littafi Mai Tsarki, kuma tana nufin "a wurinka", in ji West a baya, yayin da yake tattaunawa da mai gabatar da shirye-shiryen rediyo Big Boy game da sunan faifan nasa.
"Wannan ni ne kai, wannan mu ne, wannan mu ne".
Na canza sunana daga Kany, wanda yake nufin "wanda yake ɗaya" zuwa Ye, wanda yake nufin nagarta da mugunta, da rikice-rikice da kuma sauran abubuwa.
Wannan kundin yana nuna irin mutumin da muke.
Kanye West ba shi ne kawai mai rairayi da ke yin amfani da sunansa ba.
Sean Combs an fi saninsa da Puff Daddy, P. Diddy, ko Diddy, amma a wannan shekarar, mawaƙin ya ce ya fi son Love da Brother Love.
