LeBron zai buga wasan farko na Lakers a San Diego ranar Lahadi
Magoya baya da yawa ba za su jira har sai LeBron James ya buga wa Los Angeles Lakers wasa ba.
Kocin Lakers, Luke Walton, ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan farko a ranar Lahadi da Denver Nuggets a San Diego.
Amma ba a san adadin lokacin da ya yi wasa ba.
"Wannan shi ne fiye da daya da kuma a karkashin 48," ya ce a Walton Lakers official website.
Mai ba da rahoto a Lakers Mike Trudell ya ce James zai buga wasan da aka ƙidaya.
Bayan an gama wasan motsa jiki a makon da ya gabata, an tambayi James game da shirinsa na sake buga wasanni shida a kakar wasan farko na Lakers.
"Ba na bukatar wasan farko a wannan lokaci a rayuwata don in wartsake", in ji shi.
A wani taron yakin neman zaben Trump a West Virginia, a tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara jerin tarurrukansa na neman zabe a wannan dare a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko na ayyukan yakin neman zaben Trump da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da ake jiran zaben tabbatar da kujerar shugaban kasa, Trump zai zabi wanda zai nada a matsayin sabon alkalin kotun, yana kuma kokarin kara yawan goyon baya a zaben da ke tafe, saboda 'yan Republican na ganin cewa za su rasa ikon da suke da shi a majalisa, bayan zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi taron neman zaben shugaban kasa a yammacin Virginia, kuma ta yaya za a iya kallon shi a yanar gizo?
Za a yi taron kamfen din Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, a daren yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018, da misalin karfe 7 na yamma agogon gabas.
Za a iya kallon yakin neman zaben Trump na West Virginia ta yanar gizo ta hanyar YouTube.
Da alama dai Trump zai yi magana ne a kan wanda ya yi takarar shugabancin kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, a kan zaman kotun da ya yi tsami a makon nan, wanda ya fuskanci tashin hankali a kan zargin da ake yi masa na cin zarafin 'yan mata, yayin da kuma aka dakatar da amincewa da kujerar majalisar dattawa na mako guda, a yayin da hukumar binciken FBI ke ci gaba da bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan jerin kamfen din shi ne ya taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar babban zabe a watan Nuwamba.
Shugaba Trump ya ce shirin da aka yi na mako biyar da ya gabata, ya yi niyyar jan hankalin masu sa kai da magoya baya, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjayen da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da kuma majalisar dattawa.
"Gudanar da majalisa yana da matukar muhimmanci ga shugaban kasa, Trump zai shiga cikin yakin neman zabe, yana shiga cikin jihohi da dama", in ji wani jami'in yakin neman zaben Trump, wanda bai so a ambaci sunansa ba.
Taron kamfen na daren yau, wanda aka shirya zai gudana a filin wasa na Wesbank a Wheeling, na iya kawo masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, da kuma samun rahoto a kafafen watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, in ji West Virginia News Metro.
A ranar Asabar, Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia a karo na biyu a cikin wata guda, jihar da ya samu fiye da kashi 40 cikin 100 na masu jefa kuri'a a 2016.
Trump na kokarin taimakawa dan takarar shugaban kasa a majalisar dattawa Patrick Morrisy, dan West Virginia, wanda ke kan gaba a zaben shugaban kasa.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrissey cewa shugaban kasa ya zo don ya karfafa sakamakon da ya samu", in ji masanin kimiyyar siyasa Simon Haeder na jami'ar West Virginia, in ji Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Ƙungiyar 'yan wasan Amurka ta yi farin ciki da wannan gasa, suna da kwarin gwiwa a wasan da za a yi ranar Lahadi
Bayan wasanni uku na wasa guda, wasannin da aka buga a ranar Asabar da yamma sun kasance daidai abin da ake bukata a gasar Ryder.
Matsayi mai juyawa mai juyawa yana da ma'ana mai ban mamaki a cikin wasanni, amma 'yan wasa suna da gaskiya a cikin wannan, musamman ma a wasanni kamar wannan.
To, ina suke ganin za a sami canji a yanzu?
"Sun yi ta kan gaba da maki shida, wanda yanzu ya zama hudu, don haka ina ganin zan iya daukar wannan a matsayin karamin juyi", in ji Jordan Spieth a karshen ranar.
