Spieth ya ce, "Amurkawa suna jin cewa ba su da isasshen iskar da za su iya hurawa, amma suna da kwarin gwiwa, musamman a tsakanin Spieth da Justin Thomas, waɗanda suka yi wasa tare duk rana, kuma kowannensu ya samu maki uku daga cikin hudu".
Spieth ya kasance mai haƙuri a kan duka biyu, kuma ya nuna misali.
Wannan muryar ta'aziyya ta ƙara ƙara a kowane zagaye, ta rufe ƙwallon ƙwallon ƙwallon ƙwallon da zai sa a yi wasa na huɗu bayan da ya yi nasara da Thomas.
Wurin da ya lashe wasan a karo na 15 ya yi irin wannan kukan, wanda ya nuna imaninsa cewa, Amurkawa ba su daina gasar ba.
Spieth ya ce, "Ya kamata ka mai da hankali sosai wajen wasa da kuma kula da wasan da kake yi".
Wannan shi ne abin da 'yan wasan za su iya yi.
18 don a yi alama.
'Yan wasan da suka fi Spieth da Thomas a kwana biyu a jere sune Francesco Molinar da Tommy Fleetwood, 'yan wasan da ba a yi musu ba a gasar Ryder Cup.
Ƙungiyar Turai na ban mamaki amma suna ƙaunar juna suna da huɗu daga cikin huɗu kuma babu abin da zai iya tafiya ba daidai ba.
Moliwood ne kawai ma'aurata da ba su buga a ranar Asabar da yamma bogey, guje bogeys kuma a ranar Asabar da safe, a ranar Jumma'a da yamma da kuma a baya a karfe tara na ranar Jumma'a da safe.
Wasan da kuma yadda suke kwarara da karfin su a cikin wannan taron jama'a da kuma daga can, ya kara tabbatar da cewa 'yan wasan da za su fafata a ranar Lahadi, kuma idan rana ta fito a filin wasa na Le Golf National, babu wani dan wasan da ya fi Fleetwood ko Molinar da ya san da nasarar da 'yan wasan Turai za su samu.
Da farko, an yi amfani da shi a cikin ɗakunan da ke da ɗakuna biyu.
Amma faɗin cewa Turai za ta yi fice ya yi tsayi.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun yi saurin kai Sergio Garcia, gwarzon 'yan wasa hudu na wannan safiya, a wasan da ya yi da Alex Noren.
Bogey da 'yan wasa biyu a cikin tara na farko sun jefa ɗan Spaniard da ɗan Sweden cikin rami mai zurfi da ba su da wani bege na samun kansu.
Amma a ranar Asabar, ba wanda zai fito da kai daga ramin.
Wasanni kamar na kwando da kuma na biyu, yana da ban sha'awa sosai idan aka yi la'akari da yadda abokan hulɗa suke tattaunawa da kuma yadda ake ba da shawara da kuma ba da shawara da kuma yadda yanayin zai iya canjawa a kowane lokaci.
Turai ta fi kowane kungiya kyau a baya kuma ta yi nasara a wasan karshe, amma wannan wasa da aka yi a cikin hudu ya nuna cewa Amurka ta yi rawar jiki a wasan da wasu, musamman Amurkawa, suka yi shakkarsa.
Turai za ta yi nasara a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup 106
Turai za ta yi nasara a wasan karshe na Ryder Cup, inda za ta yi nasara a kan Amurka 10-6 bayan wasan kwallon kafa da kuma wasan dab da kwallo a ranar Asabar.
Ƙwararrun 'yan wasa biyu, Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun ci nasara biyu a kan Tiger Woods, wanda ya yi fama da wahala, don ya kara maki hudu a gasar Le Golf National.
Bayan rashin nasara, tawagar Amurka ta yi nasara a wasan farko da ta yi nasara da ci 3-1.
A wasan farko, Amurka ta kara da cewa ta ci wasanni biyu, amma ba ta iya cike ragamar da ta rasa ba.
Jim Furyk zai ci 8 a wasan mako 12 da aka buga ranar Lahadi don ya ci kofin.
Fleetwood ne na farko a Turai da ya lashe da maki hudu a jere, tare da Molinara, wanda aka sani da Molliwood bayan karshen mako, su ne biyu a tarihin Ryder Cup da suka lashe maki hudu a wasansu na hudu.
Bayan sun kashe Woods da Patrick Reed da 'yan bindiga hudu, sun ci gaba da wannan hali, sun ci nasara a kan Woods da kuma dan wasan farko na Amurka Bryson Dechambeau da 'yan bindiga biyar zuwa hudu.
Woods, wanda ya yi nasara a wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna haskensa na rashin nasara, amma yanzu ya yi hasararsa na 29 a wasan kwallaye hudu da kuma 19 a wasan da ya yi a wasan da aka yi a kwallaye biyu, inda ya ci nasara a wasanni bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda ya fito da kansa a matsayin dan wasa na hudu a safiyar yau, ya dawo tare da abokin aiki Henrik Stenson a wasan da suka yi, inda suka ci Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka, wadanda suke na daya da na uku a duniya, da ci 2 da 1.
A Turai, ba a yi nasara ba, ko da yake an yi gasar ne a wata rana mai kyau da iska a kudancin Paris.
A ranar Asabar, Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas, wanda ya lashe gasar sau uku, sun ba wa 'yan wasan Amurka da ke gasar maki biyu.
Sun samu nasara a wasan kwallon kafa hudu da suka yi da ci 2-1 a kan Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter na Spain, suka dawo daga baya suka ci Poulter da Rory McIlroyd 4-3 a wasan da suka yi a raga, bayan sun yi rashin nasara a raga biyu.
Sau biyu ne kawai a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup, wata kungiya ta yi nasarar dawowa daga rashin cin maki hudu ta shiga wasan farko, duk da cewa a matsayinta na mai mallakar gasar, bangaren Furyk yana bukatar kawai a yi masa kwallo don ya ci gaba da cin kofin.
