A cewar Washington Examiner, idan ya cancanta, Washington za ta iya amfani da sojojinta na ruwa don kauce wa cin zarafin kasuwar makamashin Rasha, ciki har da yankin gabas ta tsakiya, kamar yadda Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida Ryan Zinke ya bayyana.
Zinke ya yi ikirarin cewa shigar Rasha a Syria, musamman idan ta yi hakan ne a gayyatar da wata gwamnati mai bin doka da oda ta yi, ya yi amfani da shi wajen neman sabbin kasuwannin samar da makamashi.
"Ina tsammanin dalilin da yasa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne suna son samar da makamashi kamar yadda suke yi a Gabashin Turai, a kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
Kuma bisa ga yadda wani jami'in ya ce, akwai hanyoyi da kuma hanyoyin da za a magance wannan.
Amurka na da wannan damar ta amfani da sojojin ruwanmu don tabbatar da cewa an bude hanyoyin ruwa kuma idan ya zama dole, an toshe su don tabbatar da cewa makamashin su ba zai shiga kasuwa ba", in ji shi.
Sanarwar ta Zink ta kasance ne ga mahalarta taron da kungiyar masu amfani da makamashi ta Consumer Energy Alliance, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta, wacce ita ce muryar masu amfani da makamashi a Amurka.
Ya ci gaba da kwatanta hanyoyin da Washington ke bi wajen magance Rasha da Iran, yana mai cewa, "ainihin iri daya ne".
"Zaɓin tattalin arziƙin Iran da Rasha ya fi ko ƙasa da, haɓaka da sauya mai", in ji shi, yayin da yake mai da Rasha "karamar doki mai wayo" wanda tattalin arzikinsa ya dogara da burbushin mai.
Wannan magana na zuwa ne a daidai lokacin da gwamnatin Trump ke da burin kara yawan iskar gas zuwa kasashen Turai, inda za a maye gurbin Rasha da ke da tsada mai yawa ga masu amfani da gas a Turai.
Don yin hakan, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump da kansa, suna kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta hana shi "kwakwarwar" aikin bututun Nord Stream 2, wanda Trump ya ce ya mayar da Berlin "gidan fursuna" ga Moscow.
Moscow ta sha nanata cewa aikin fam biliyan 11 na Nord Stream 2 wanda zai ninka na yanzu zuwa mita biliyan 110 na mai, aikin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
Gwamnatin ta Kremlin ta ce, tsananin adawar da Washington ta yi wa wannan aikin, ya samo asali ne daga dalilai na tattalin arziki, kuma ya nuna cewa, ba a bin doka ba.
"Ina ganin mun yarda cewa makamashi ba zai zama hanyar yin amfani da karfi ba, kuma ya kamata masu amfani da makamashi su sami damar zabar masu samar da shi", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha, Aleksandr Novak, a wani taro da ya yi da Ministan Makamashi na Amurka, Rick Perry, a Moscow a watan Satumban da ya gabata.
A halin da Amurka ta nuna a wannan batu, Jamus ta sake jaddada aniyarta na tallafa wa wannan shiri.
Ƙungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus, BDI, ta yi kira ga Amurka ta guje wa manufofin makamashi na EU da kuma yarjejeniyar Berlin da Moscow.
"Ina da babbar matsala idan wata kasa ta uku ta shiga cikin samar mana da makamashi", in ji Dieter Kempf, shugaban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus (BDI), bayan ganawar da suka yi kwanan nan tsakanin shugabar gwamnatin Jamus Angela Merkel da shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin.
Elizabeth Warren na da niyyar tsayawa takarar shugabancin kasa a 2020, in ji Sanata daga Massachusetts
A ranar Asabar, 'yar majalisar dattawa Elizabeth Warren ta Massachusetts ta ce tana da niyyar tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa a zaben da za a yi na 'yan watanni masu zuwa.
A cikin majalisun garin Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ya tabbatar da cewa yana tunanin sake tsayawa takara.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington domin gyara karyayyar gwamnatinmu, kuma wannan ya hada da uwargidan shugaban kasa", in ji ta a wani jawabi da ta yi a The Hill.
"Bayan 6 ga Nuwamba, zan yi tunani sosai game da tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa".
Warren ya kuma yi tsokaci a kan ayyukan da Shugaba Donald Trump ke yi a fadar shugaban kasa, yana mai cewa, shugaban na tura kasar nan zuwa hanyar da ba ta dace ba.
"Ina matukar damuwa game da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokradiyyarmu", in ji shi.
Warren ya yi ta sukar Trump da kuma dan takararsa na Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh.
A ranar Juma'a, Warren ya rubuta cewa, "Tabbas za mu bukaci binciken FBI kafin a kada kuri'ar".
Amma kuma, a wani binciken da aka fitar a ranar Alhamis, an gano cewa yawancin 'yan adawar Warren ba su yarda ya tsaya takara a 2020.
A cewar wani bincike da jami'ar Suffolk ta yi da kuma Boston Globe, kashi 58 cikin 100 na masu zaɓe a Massachusetts sun ce bai kamata ya tsaya takara ba.
Kashi 32 cikin 100 sun goyi bayan wannan takara.
Binciken ya nuna goyon baya ga tsohon gwamna Deval Patrick, tare da kashi 38% na goyon bayan yiwuwar takara, kuma 48% sun yi adawa da shi.
Sauran manyan sunayen 'yan Democrat da aka tattauna dangane da yiwuwar takarar 2020 sun hada da tsohon mataimakin shugaban kasa Joe Biden da kuma Sanata Bernie Sanders na Vermont.
Biden ya ce zai yanke shawara a hukumance a watan Janairu, in ji kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press.
Sarah Palin ta yi tsokaci a taron Donald Trump game da PTSD na Track Palin
Palin mai shekara 26 ya yi shekara guda a Iraki bayan da aka kwashe shi a watan Satumba.
An kama shi a ranar Litinin da dare a kan wani laifi na cin zarafin mata da maza.
"Abin da ɗana ke fuskanta, abin da ya fuskanta a lokacin da ya dawo, na iya danganta kaina da sauran iyalai waɗanda ke jin tasirin PTSD da raunukan da sojojinmu ke dawowa da shi, "in ji shi a gaban masu sauraro a taron Donald Trump a Tulsa Oktaham.
Palin ya kira kama ɗansa "gidan giwa" kuma ya ce game da ɗansa da sauran tsoffin sojan, "Za su dawo da ɗan bambanci, za su dawo da ƙyamar gaske, za su dawo da tunanin ko an girmama abin da sojoji da matukan jirgin sama da sauran sojoji suka ba ƙasar. "
An kama shi a ranar Litinin a Wasilla, Alaska, kuma a cewar Dan Bennett, mai magana da yawun 'yan sanda na Wasilla, an zarge shi da cin zarafin mata a gida, da shiga tsakani a cikin rahoton cin zarafin mata, da kuma mallakar makami a cikin maye.
Jihohi 18 da kuma gundumar Columbia sun yi adawa da sabuwar dokar mafaka
Kasashe goma sha takwas da kuma gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan ƙalubalen doka kan sabuwar dokar Amurka da ta hana ba da mafaka ga waɗanda ke tserewa daga ɓarnar da ake yi musu ko kuma tashin hankali na cikin gida.
Wakilan kasashe da yankuna 18 sun gabatar da wata takarda a gaban kotun a Washington a ranar Juma'a don tallafawa manufofin da ke kira ga masu neman mafaka, in ji NBC News.
An kasa bayyana cikakken sunan mai gabatar da kara a shari'ar Grace v. Sessions, wadda kungiyar kare hakkin bil'adama ta Amurka ta gabatar a watan Agusta, a kan manufofin gwamnatin tarayya.
Matar ta ce wani abokin aikinta da kuma 'ya'yanta 'yan bindiga masu taurin kai sun yi mata fyade, amma jami'an Amurka sun ki amincewa da bukatarta ta neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga watan Yuli.
An kama shi a jihar Texas.
Lauyoyin da ke goyon bayan Grace sun bayyana El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala a matsayin kasashen da ke kawo yawan 'yan gudun hijira zuwa Amurka, wadanda ke da babbar matsala ta 'yan daba da kuma tashin hankali na gida.
Sabuwar manufar mafaka ta Amurka ta sauya hukuncin da aka yanke a 2014 na Hukumar da ke Kula da Daukaka Kara game da Shige da Fice, wanda ya ba da izinin baƙi ba tare da izini ba don neman mafaka daga tashin hankali na gida.
Babban mai shari'a na gundumar Columbia, Karl Racine, ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa a ranar Juma'a cewa sabuwar manufar "ta yi watsi da shekarun da suka gabata na dokokin ƙasa, na tarayya da na ƙasa da ƙasa".
'Dokar tarayya ta bukaci a yi hukunci a kan dukkan neman mafaka bisa ga takamaiman gaskiya da yanayin da ake nema, kuma wannan bukata ta saɓa wa wannan ka'ida,' in ji taƙaitaccen bayanin da abokan kotu suka bayar.
A cikin wata sanarwa, lauyoyin sun kuma yi ikirarin cewa hana baƙi shiga Amurkawa zai cutar da tattalin arzikin Amurka, suna cewa za su iya zama 'yan kasuwa da' samar da aikin da ake buƙata. '
A watan Yuni, Babban Shari'a Jeff Sessions ya umurci alƙalan shige da fice su daina ba da mafaka ga duk wanda ya tsere wa cin zarafin mata ko kuma cin zarafin jama'a.
"Binciken mafaka na da damar da za a bai wa wadanda suka bar kasarsu saboda tsoron tsanantawa ko kuma tsoron da suka ji kan launin fata, addini, kabilanci ko kuma wata kungiya ko ra'ayi na siyasa", in ji Sessions a sanarwarsa ta ranar 11 ga Yuni.
Ba a taɓa kafa mafaka domin a magance dukan matsaloli - ko da matsaloli masu tsanani - da mutane suke fuskanta kowace rana.
