Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da yin amfani da tallace-tallace na 'yancin kai'
Bayan mako guda da wata jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wata takarda mai shafi hudu a shafin jaridar Daily News na Amurka, tana mai cewa, cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da Sin na da amfani, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da yin amfani da kafofin yada labaran Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana a ranar Laraba game da karin kudin da China Daily ta biya a jaridar Des Moines Register, jaridar da ta fi yawan masu karantawa a Iowa, bayan da aka zargi China da yin kutse a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka da aka yi a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, abin da China ta musanta.
Zargin da Trump ya yi na cewa Beijing ta yi kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka, ya nuna abin da jami'an Amurka suka bayyana wa kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters a matsayin wani sabon mataki a wani kamfen da Washington ke yi na matsa wa China lamba.
Yayin da yake da kyau gwamnatocin kasashen waje su rika tallata tallafin da ke inganta cinikayya, Beijing da Washington na cikin wani gagarumin yaƙin cinikayya da ke ci gaba da yin daidai da jadawalin kuɗin da ake shigo da shi.
China ta dauki matakan mayar da martani a farkon yakin da aka yi da kwastan da aka yi niyyar kama masu fitar da kayayyaki daga jihohi kamar Iowa, saboda sun goyi bayan jam'iyyun Republican na Trump, in ji masana na Sin da Amurka.
Jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, kuma babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona na China, Terry Branstad, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
A cikin wata sanarwa a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi, Branstad ya rubuta cewa: "A yanzu, kasar Sin ta ninka matsin da take yi ta hanyar buga tallace-tallacen da ke nuna cewa tana da 'yanci a jaridarmu".
"A yada farfagandarsu, gwamnatin China ta yi amfani da 'yancin fadin albarkacin baki da kuma' yan jaridu na Amurka, ta hanyar sanya talla a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
Amma a cikin 'yan bindigar Beijing, akwai murya kaɗan kuma ba za a iya ganin bambancin ra'ayi da gaske da jama'ar kasar Sin za su iya samu game da yanayin tattalin arzikin kasar Sin ba, yayin da kafofin watsa labarai ke karkashin ikon kwaminisanci na jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin, in ji shi.
Ya daɗa cewa wata jarida a ƙasar ta ƙi buga labarinsa, amma bai faɗi takamaiman jaridar ba.
Masu sharhi sun yi gargadin cewa 'yan Republican za su janye mata masu zabe kafin zaben tsakiyar shekara ta 2020 sakamakon rashin nasarar Kavanaugh.
Yayin da 'yan Republican ke jiran a kare dan takarar da ke neman a yi masa shari'a a kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ake zarginsa da laifin cin zarafin mata da dama, masu sharhi a kan al'amuran siyasa sun yi gargadin cewa za a yi masa fatali a zaben da ke tafe, musamman daga bangaren mata.
Ra'ayoyin da ke kewaye da wannan lamari sun kasance a cikin ruwa, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun riga sun nuna cewa suna son ci gaba da jefa kuri'a.
Ba za a iya janye irin wannan abu ba, in ji Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin kimiyyar siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell da ke Jami'ar Syracuse, a wata kasida da aka wallafa a ranar Asabar a The Hill.
Reeher ya yi amannar cewa, wani abu da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya yi a minti na karshe, dangane da binciken da FBI ke yi, zai kwantar da hankalin masu jefa kuri'a.
"'Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba - ba za su manta ba gobe ko a watan Nuwamba", in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara kuma wakilin ƙasar na MoveOn, a ranar Juma'a, a cewar jaridar Washington DC.
A safiyar yau Juma'a, masu zanga-zangar sun ce "Nuwamba na zuwa!" a wani zanga-zanga a harabar majalisar dattijai, saboda 'yan Republican, wadanda ke da iko a kan kwamitocin shari'a, sun yanke shawarar ci gaba da takarar Kavanaugh duk da shaidar da Dr. Christine Blasey Ford ta bayar, in ji Mic.
'Democratic India da kuma 'cikin gida's sake' zai fara fita daga jadawalin, in ji Stu Rothenberg, wani mai nazarin al'amuran siyasa a zaman kansa.
Mutane suna cewa yana da tsayi, kuma hakan gaskiya ne.
Amma kuma yana iya zama mafi girma, musamman ma a tsakanin mata masu jefa kuri'a da kuma 'yan shekaru 18 zuwa 29, waɗanda ba sa son shugaban kuma sukan ƙi jefa kuri'a.
Ko da kafin Ford ya ba da shaida a bainar jama'a game da zarginsa na yin lalata da dan takarar da ya yi wa babban alkalin kotun, masana na tunanin cewa za a samu koma baya idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da yin magana.
"Ya zama abin takaici ga GOP", a farkon makon da ya gabata, Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican na kasa, ya ce, a cewar NBC News.
"Ba wai kawai game da zaben kwamitin ba, zaben karshe, ko kuma ko Kavanaugh zai yi aiki, yana da game da yadda 'yan Republican suka yi da kuma yadda suka bi da shi", Priorities USA (wani rukuni da ke taimaka wa 'yan Democrat zabar) Guy Cecil, shugaban, ya ja hankalin masu sauraron labarai.
Duk da haka, 'yan Amurkan sun nuna cewa sun banbanta da juna a kan wanda ya gaskata da Ford da kuma wanda ya yi imani da Kavanaugh, amma sun fi yarda da Kavanaugh.
Wani sabon binciken da YouGov ya yi ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 na masu amsa sun amince da furcin Ford, yayin da kashi 35 suka ce sun amince da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce sun yi imanin cewa Kavanaugh ya yi ƙarya a lokacin da yake ba da shaida, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari suka ce hakan ma ya shafi Ford.
A cewar Flake, FBI na binciken da Ford ya yi da kuma wasu zarge-zargen da ake yi wa Deborah Ramirez, in ji jaridar The Guardian.
A makon da ya gabata, a gaban kwamitin daukaka kara na majalisar dattawa, Ford ya shaida a gaban kwamitin da aka yi wa shari'a cewa Kavanaugh ya yi masa fyade a lokacin da yake da shekaru 17.
Ramirez ya yi zargin cewa dan takarar da ke neman a naɗa shi a matsayin babban mai shari'a ya nuna masa al'aurarsa ta jima'i a wani bikin da suka halarta a lokacin da suke karatu a jami'ar Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda ya kirkiro Duniyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya yana shirin kafa sabuwar hanyar sadarwa da za ta yi daidai da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya kafa kamfani mai suna Startup wanda ke kokarin yin gogayya da Facebook, Amazon, da Google.
Inrupt, wanda shine sabon aikinsa na zamani, shine kamfanin da ke gina Berners-Lee, wani tsari na tushen tushen Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su da kuma mutanen da za a ba su damar samun damar bayanai.
A wata hira da aka yi da shi a kamfanin Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi ba'a cewa burin Inrupt shi ne "mulkin duniya".
"Ya kamata mu yi shi yanzu", ya ce game da fara.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasaha na Solidi don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar database na kan layi ko POD.
Zai iya zama jerin sunayen masu tuntuba, jerin abubuwan da za a yi, kalandar, tarin waƙoƙi da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na ƙwararru.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna aiki a cikin bincike guda kuma a lokaci guda.
Abin da ya sa wannan keɓaɓɓen bayanan kan layi ya zama na musamman shi ne cewa mai amfani zai iya zaɓar wanda zai iya samun damar wannan bayanin.
Kamfanin ya kira shi don ba da izini na sirri ta hanyar bayanai.
A cewar shugaban kamfanin John Bruce, manufar Inrupt ita ce kamfanin ya samar da albarkatu, tsari da kuma gwanintar da ta dace don taimakawa samar da Solid ga kowa.
A halin yanzu, kamfanin ya kunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, da wani tsarin tsaro da aka saya daga IBM, da wasu masu kirkirar da aka yi hayar su don yin aiki a kan aikin, da kuma al'umma masu ba da agaji.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu haɓaka fasaha a duk faɗin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da ma'aikatansa ba sa tattaunawa da Facebook da Google kan ko za su kawo sauyi na dindindin ba, idan an yi amfani da dukkan tsarin kasuwancin su a cikin dare.
Ba mu nemi izinin su ba.
A wani sako da ya wallafa a Medium a ranar Alhamis, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa Inrupt yana da burin samar da makamashi da kuma tsarin halittu don taimakawa wajen kare mutuncin da ingancin sabon shafin yanar gizo da aka kirkira bisa Solid.
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya canja hanyar da aka san Intanet da ita sa'ad da ya kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar gizo ta Duniya a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai ƙarfi a cikin tattaunawar 'yanci na yanar gizo.
Ko da a lokacin da Inrupt ya fara, Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da kasancewa wanda ya kafa kuma darektan World Wide Web Consortium, Web Foundation, da kuma Open Data Institute.
"Ina da matuƙar kwarin gwiwa game da sabuwar zamanin yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: an buɗe wani abin tunawa na ruhaniya da aka ba da Victoria Cross a cikin Yaƙin Duniya na I
A birnin da ake bikin cika shekara 100 da kafuwar cocin Victoria's Cross, wato, giciye da aka yi amfani da ita a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na ɗaya, ne kawai cocin da ke Ingila ya yi bikin cika shekara 100 da kafuwa.
Lieutenant Colonel Reverend Bernard Vann ya yi yaƙi don ya ba da lambar yabo a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918 a cikin harin Bellenglise da Lehaucour.
Amma bayan kwana huɗu, wani maharbi ya harbe shi kuma ya mutu, ba tare da sanin cewa ya karɓi lambar yabo mafi girma a rundunar soja ba.
'Ya'yansa maza biyu sun buɗe wani dutse mai daraja a ranar Asabar a Rushden, Northamptonshire.
Ɗaya daga cikin jikokin, Michael Vann, ya ce zai zama "abin da ya dace da a yi bikin" idan aka buɗe dutsen daidai shekara 100 bayan nasarar da kakan ya yi.
A cewar London Gazette, a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, Lieutenant Colonel Vann ya jagoranci rundunarsa ta Canal de Saint-Quentin, "a cikin wani hazo mai kauri, a cikin jerin harsasai da kuma harsashi".
Daga baya ya yi hanzari zuwa gabar, ya kai harin da "babban jarumta" kafin ya kai hari kan wani mai harbi da harsashi, ya kuma harbi abokan gaba uku.
A ranar 4 ga Oktoba, 1918, Lieutenant Colonel Vann ya mutu sanadin harin wani ɗan harin bindiga na Jamus, fiye da wata guda kafin yaƙin ya ƙare.
Michael Vann, mai shekara 72, ya ce abin da kakansa ya yi "abu ne da na sani ba zan taɓa iya maimaitawa ba, amma ina godiya a kai".
Shi da ɗan'uwansa, Dakta James Vann sun yi bikin aure bayan wani biki da wasu matasa 'yan wasan Brentwood suka yi.
Michael Vann ya ce "godiya ce a gare ni in halarci wannan biki" kuma ya ce "galibin mutane da suka halarci bikin da kuma goyon bayan da suka nuna cewa za a iya kimanta gwarzon gaske".
