Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a sakamakon girgizar kasa da tsunami da ya afku a birnin Paluch na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, in ji jami'ai, inda suka ce adadin wadanda suka mutu na karuwa.
Tun da yake babu wata hanyar sadarwa, masu aikin ceto ba su samu labari daga yankin Donggala da ke arewacin Palau ba, wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar mai girman maki 7.5.
An yi wa'azi ga mutane fiye da 16,000 da suka ƙaura daga birnin Palos bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu abubuwa masu muhimmanci game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, wanda ke kan iyakar gabar tekun Sulawesi ta yamma, kuma an kiyasta yawan jama'a na 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
Birnin ya yi bikin cika shekara 40 da kafuwa sa'ad da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku.
Yankin Donggala yanki ne da ke da nisan sama da kilomita 300 (180 mi) a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
A cikin 2017, an kiyasta yawan mutanen Regency, wani yanki na lardin, ya kai 299 200.
Kifi da noma sune manyan ayyukan tattalin arziki na lardin Central Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala.
A cikin lardin, ma'adinan nickel ma suna da mahimmanci, wanda galibi ya mai da hankali kan Morowali, gabar tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar Kula da Bala'i a Indonesia ta ce, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, sun yi ta tsunami sau da yawa a tsibiran Paluyu da Donggala.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya halaka mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje.
A shekara ta 1996, tsunami ya afka a yammacin Donggala, inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana da zurfin zurfin teku a cikin Tekun Fasifik, kuma ana girgizar ƙasa a kai a kai.
Ga wasu daga cikin girgizar ƙasa da tsunami mafi girma da aka taɓa gani a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar tekun yamma na lardin Aceh na Indonesia a Arewacin Sumatra ta haifar da tsunami, wanda ya shafi kasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: An yi girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani a yammacin Sumatra a watan Maris da kuma farkon watan Afrilu.
Mutane da yawa sun mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke kusa da Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai girman maki 6.8 ta auku a kudancin Java, tsibirin da ya fi kowa yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta jawo tsunami da ya auko a gaɓar teku ta kudu kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa yankin da ke kusa da Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai na tsibirin Sumatra, inda ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 da ta hallaka ƙauyuka da dama da kuma kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wata girgizar kasa mai zurfi ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya a Aceh, ta haifar da barna da fargaba, inda ta tunatar da mutane game da bala'in da aka yi a 2004 da girgizar kasa da tsunami.
Ko da yake ba a yi wata guguwar tsunami ba a wannan lokacin, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a gine-gine da suka rushe.
2018: Manyan girgizar kasa sun afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, inda suka kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ƙasar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta sa dubban masu yawon buɗe ido sun makale na ɗan lokaci.
