Nancy Pelosi ta kira Brett Kavanaugh "mai tsananin ra'ayi" kuma ta ce bai cancanci ya zama babban alkalin kotun ba
Shugabar 'yan adawa a majalisar wakilai, Nancy Pelosi, ta bayyana wanda za a yi wa alkalancin kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, a matsayin "mai tsananin sonta" kuma ta ce "ba shi da ingancin hali da zai iya zama alkalin kotun koli".
Pelosi ya bayyana ra'ayinsa ne a wata hira da aka yi da shi a ranar Asabar a wani bikin bikin a Texas Tribune Festival da aka yi a Austin, Texas.
Na lura cewa idan wata mace ta yi irin wannan jawabin, za a kira ta da "tsagwaron", in ji Pelosi game da yadda ta mayar da martani game da shaidar da Kavanaugh ya bayar a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa a ranar Alhamis.
Kavanaugh ya musanta zargin da aka yi masa na yin lalata da Dokta Christine Blasey Ford lokacin da suke matasa.
Kavanaugh ya kasance mai matukar damuwa a cikin jawabinsa na farko, yana da wani lokacin da ya kusan yin kururuwa yayin da yake bayanin danginsa da kuma shekarun makarantar sakandare, kuma a wasu lokuta ya kasance mai tsaurin kai.
Ya kuma yi Allah-wadai da mambobin jam'iyyar Democrat da ke kwamitin, yana mai cewa zargin da ake masa na kisan gilla ne da 'yan adawa da ke fushi da Hillary Clinton ta yi rashin nasara a zaben shugaban kasa na 2016.
A cewar Pelosi, ya yi imanin cewa shaidar da Kavanaugh ya bayar ya nuna cewa bai dace ya zama alkalin kotun koli ba, saboda ya nuna cewa yana da ra'ayin dimokradiyya.
"Ina ganin ya na bata wa kansa suna ne da irin maganganun da ya yi da kuma yadda ya yi wa 'yan Clinton da 'yan Democrat hari", in ji shi.
Pelosi ya yi ta yin shiru lokacin da aka tambaye shi ko zai yi kokarin tsige Kavanaugh idan aka tabbatar da cewa 'yan Democrat sun sami rinjaye a majalisar.
"Ina gaya muku, idan bai gaya wa 'yan majalisa da FBI gaskiya ba, ba kawai ya dace ya zama babban alkali ba, amma bai dace da kotun da yake aiki a yanzu ba", in ji Pelosi.
A yanzu dai Kavanaugh shi ne babban alkalin kotun daukaka kara na gundumar Columbia.
Pelosi ya kara da cewa a matsayinsa na dan Democrat, yana cikin damuwa game da yiwuwar hukuncin da Kavanaugh zai yanke kan dokar Affordable Care Act ko kuma Roe v. Wade, saboda ana daukarsa a matsayin mai ra'ayin mazan jiya.
